# Test Case: Submit Valid Contact Form

**Test Case ID:** TC-601  
**Feature:** Contact Form â€“ loveable.dev  
**Test Type:** Functional (Positive Case)  
**Priority:** High  
**Created by:** Sharnelle Guthrie  
**Date:** June 11, 2025

---

## Objective  
To confirm that the contact form submits successfully when all required fields contain valid input.

---

## Preconditions  
- User is on the Contact page  
- Contact form fields are visible: Name, Email, Message, Company's website

---

## Test Steps

| Step # | Action                        | Expected Result                        |
|--------|-------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| 1      | Enter valid Name              | Name is accepted                       |
| 2      | Enter valid Email             | Email is accepted                      |                     
| 3      | Enter company website URL     | Website URL is accepted                |
| 3      | Enter a brief message         | Message is accepted                    |
| 4      | Click Submit                  | Confirmation message is displayed      |

---

## Notes  
- Success message should appear without page reload
- Form fields may reset after submission
